(C) Placing a telephone call to a consumer who has placed
his or her contact information on a national "Do-Not-Call" registry
established and maintained by the Federal Trade Commission under 16 C.F.R. §
310.4, as it existed on January 1, 2025; or
(D) Knowingly or negligently using information from a
mortgage trigger lead."
